{"tid":1883992,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［多圖］理大圍城三個月","createTime":"2020-02-17T10:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T15:49:55.000Z","uid":167544,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7c5bb067b72660160b60e924dd3bf014955767f4","tid":1883992,"uid":167544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:20:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>抗疫未忘抗戰中，驀然回首仍激動。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我諗唔駛提醒都知道我哋未嬴，當日被圍城內兄弟身心受創或被補被登記<br />\n外邊營救者們亦同樣，即使未能落場的仍不免憂心忡忡徹夜難眠。<br />\n希望透過呢套相集，喚起一點記憶。為當日的事情討回公道。亦不教當日被補手足孤單。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/puPEq61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpuPEq61.jpg&h=8ea923b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qNThXdM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqNThXdM.jpg&h=a90bacd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hgiRhdQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhgiRhdQ.jpg&h=56a0acc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dTL4CdT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdTL4CdT.jpg&h=0148bad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGiee0E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGiee0E.jpg&h=ba5f3863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H1X28kJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1X28kJ.jpg&h=aa8fb40a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JkSiGFN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJkSiGFN.jpg&h=a28f6a85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pOJUZsw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpOJUZsw.jpg&h=371c1cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zo5wheh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZo5wheh.jpg&h=055897b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#未獲公道平反<br />\n#關注被補人士<br />\n<br />\nFB 原Link: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/975774939193634/posts/2464613786976401/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F975774939193634%2Fposts%2F2464613786976401%2F&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=0bfa5843\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/975774939193634/posts/2464613786976401/</a><br />\n黃色KOL100應戰中"},{"pid":"e5ba763f222a3af67a132e704224ec26b423542e","tid":1883992,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"我諗依世仔都唔會忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3b1cc5ae8ce3f9574bfd7f571e3342b3a92eeb","tid":1883992,"uid":264074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010698c372c0e16808adf140e6d9574dd4f864c7","tid":1883992,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408774494cdde125e28edc307357878568f99e71","tid":1883992,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:10:23.000Z","msg":"睇返好心痛 唔可以比班手足白白犧牲<br />\n香港人堅持到底呀"},{"pid":"d15fe963689bc2773a04b38c86ad3dd4e2b76f9b","tid":1883992,"uid":177150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071e201c3def1287f6bd49152ca2e9ccd777a06d","tid":1883992,"uid":21285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa